---

<section
  class="hero-section relative overflow-hidden"
  aria-label="Josef Anolin — Stand-Up Comedian"
>
  <h1 class="sr-only">
    Josef Anolin — Stand-Up Comedian
  </h1>

  <div class="hero-comp">
    <img
      src="/joe-hero.png"
      alt=""
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="hero-portrait select-none pointer-events-none"
    />
    <div class="hero-logo-wrap">
      <img
        src="/joe-logo.png"
        alt="Josef Anolin — Stand Up Comedian"
        class="hero-logo select-none pointer-events-none"
      />
      <a href="#contact" class="hero-cta">BOOK ME</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="hero-bio">
    From Oakland, California currently living in Los Angeles, Josef has opened
    for the likes of Tom Segura, Whitney Cummings, and Michael Che. He likes
    telling irreverent stories based on his life and observations. He has an
    Android phone because he likes pissing you off with his green text bubbles.
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    background: #000;
    height: 100%;
    /* 200px from window-top to subject's hat / 250px guard at bottom.
       Locked at 1080+ viewports; shrinks proportionally on shorter ones. */
    padding-top: clamp(120px, 20dvh, 200px);
    padding-bottom: clamp(160px, 25dvh, 250px);
    padding-left: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 5rem);
    padding-right: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 5rem);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  /* COMP — portrait + logo overlap in the same grid cell. Sized
     primarily by WIDTH so vertical resizes don't shrink them
     drastically. Both images carry a soft dvh-based max-height that
     activates only on short viewports (≲ 1080) so bio + 40px gap
     still fits inside the 250 bottom guard. */
  .hero-comp {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: 1fr;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* Portrait — anchored right, width-only sizing (no dvh-based cap)
     so vertical resizes don't shrink it. Behavior matches the logo.
     margin-right shifts the portrait LEFT, increasing overlap with the
     logo so the title sits ON TOP of the figure's shoulder/chest. */
  .hero-portrait {
    grid-column: 1;
    grid-row: 1;
    justify-self: end;
    align-self: start;
    width: 42%;
    max-width: 540px;
    height: auto;
    margin-right: 150px;
    display: block;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* Logo + button — shifted toward center so logo OVERLAPS portrait's
     left edge by ~7%. */
  .hero-logo-wrap {
    grid-column: 1;
    grid-row: 1;
    justify-self: start;
    align-self: start;
    margin-left: 5%;
    width: 60%;
    max-width: 660px;
    z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .hero-logo {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  /* CTA — sits inside .hero-logo-wrap so its center matches the logo's center. */
  .hero-cta {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #000;
    font-family: var(--font-display), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: filter 0.18s ease, transform 0.18s ease;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .hero-cta:hover {
    filter: brightness(1.08);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* BIO — pinned to bottom of section flex container, center-aligned.
     margin-top: auto pushes bio to the bottom guard.
     padding-top: 40px enforces a minimum 40px gap above the text when
     the layout is crowded. No vertical accent rule. */
  .hero-bio {
    margin: 0;
    margin-top: auto;
    padding: 40px 0 0 0;
    font-family: var(--font-body), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 22px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: rgb(229 229 229);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 60ch;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    align-self: center;
  }

  /* MOBILE — portrait on top, then logo (overlapping portrait), then bio. */
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .hero-section {
      /* Pull all hero content up 50px (nav above the section is unaffected
         because it's outside the section). Subtract 50 from the clamped
         desktop value: clamp(120, 20dvh, 200) - 50 = clamp(70, calc(20dvh - 50px), 150). */
      padding-top: clamp(70px, calc(20dvh - 50px), 150px);
    }
    .hero-comp {
      grid-template-rows: auto auto;
      row-gap: 0;
    }
    .hero-portrait {
      grid-column: 1;
      grid-row: 1;
      justify-self: center;
      align-self: center;
      /* +30% over the prior 78% / 364px sizing. */
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 473px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    .hero-logo-wrap {
      grid-column: 1;
      grid-row: 2;
      justify-self: center;
      margin-left: 0;
      /* Pull the title (and BOOK ME beneath it) up. -60 → -105 → -140
         after the latest 35px raise. */
      margin-top: -140px;
      width: 92%;
      max-width: 480px;
    }
    .hero-cta {
      letter-spacing: 0;
      font-size: 1.2rem;       /* +3px over the desktop 1rem */
      padding: 0.55rem 1.4rem; /* less padding than desktop 0.85rem / 2rem */
    }
    .hero-bio {
      max-width: 100%;
      /* -2px from the prior 16px = 14px, lighter gray, and tighter line-height. */
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgb(180 180 180);
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
  }
</style>
